Aevum is a modified GPLv3 derivative of GPUOwl/PRPLL.

GPUOwl was originally authored by Mihai Preda:
https://github.com/preda/gpuowl

The imported base is George Woltman's GPUOwl/PRPLL fork:
https://github.com/gwoltman/gpuowl
commit 294cc485ac8cf53c8b69144a3039832eda573849

George Woltman's upstream README credits NTT and other optimizations to George Woltman and the CUDA backend to Sherpa.

The register-engine design is inspired by Marin by Yves Gallot:
https://github.com/galloty/marin

